<p class="ayah 27-57" id="57" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَنجَيْنَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So We saved him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَهْلَهُۥٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his family,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱمْرَأَتَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his wife;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدَّرْنَـٰهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We destined her</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to be) of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغَـٰبِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who remained behind.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>57<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 27-58" id="58" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَمْطَرْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And We rained</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّطَرًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a rain,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and was evil</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَطَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) rain</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُنذَرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(on) those who were warned.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>58<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
