<p class="ayah 27-60" id="60" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنزَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and sent down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sky</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآءً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">water?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَنۢبَتْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And We caused to grow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thereby</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَدَآئِقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">gardens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَاتَ بَهْجَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of beauty (and delight),</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُنۢبِتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you cause to grow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَجَرَهَآ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their trees.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَءِلَـٰهٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Is there any god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) a people</span></span><span class="word staticWo